#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:796
msgid "What is a server?"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:797
msgid "A server is a powerful, always-on computer that stores and runs the Jitsi software, allowing users to connect and hold video meetings from anywhere in the world. Think of it as the \"home\" for your meeting system that stays online 24/7."
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:800
msgid "What is a self-hosted FlexMeeting server?"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:801
msgid "A self-hosted Jitsi server means the entire video conferencing system runs on your own server or hosting environment, not on Jitsi’s public infrastructure. This gives you full control, privacy, and customization flexibility."
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:804
msgid "Why should I use a self-hosted Jitsi server instead of using public Jitsi?"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:805
msgid "Public Jitsi servers are shared, limited, and not secure for professional use. With self-hosting, you get: <br>- Enhanced privacy <br>- Better performance <br>- No limitations on usage <br>- Your own branding and domain <br>- Control over features and integrations"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:808
msgid "What do you provide in this service?"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:809
msgid "- We set up a Jitsi server on your VPS/cloud <br>- Secure it with SSL and firewalls <br>- Brand it with your logo and domain (optional) <br>- Integrate it into your website <br>- Provide admin access and documentation <br>- Offer post-installation support if needed"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:812
msgid "Do I need technical knowledge to maintain the server?"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:813
msgid "No. We handle everything during setup. If you opt for our support plan, we also handle maintenance, upgrades, and any issues that arise."
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:816
msgid "What are the server requirements?"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:817
msgid "Minimum requirements: <br>- Ubuntu/Debian VPS <br>- 4+ CPU cores <br>- 8GB+ RAM <br>- 100 Mbps+ bandwidth <br>We’ll guide you to choose the right hosting based on your expected usage."
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:820
msgid "Can I use this with my existing website or LMS?"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:821
msgid "Yes. We can integrate Jitsi into any website, including WordPress, Moodle, TutorLMS, LearnDash, or even custom-built platforms."
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:824
msgid "How long does it take to set everything up?"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:825
msgid "Typically between 1–3 business days, depending on your customization and hosting setup."
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:828
msgid "Can I record meetings or stream them?"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:829
msgid "Yes, we can enable recording (using Jibri) and YouTube live streaming on request. Note that these features require additional server resources."
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:832
msgid "Is it one-time setup or recurring service?"
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:833
msgid "The setup is one-time unless you choose our optional support & maintenance plan for updates, backups, and ongoing help."
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin/mannage-callback.php:836
